Extract:
- title: Clean, concise task title
- project: Best-guess project name (e.g., 'Second Brain', 'Work', 'Personal', 'Health', 'Finance')
- priority: One of 'Critical', 'High', 'Medium', 'Low' based on urgency cues
- tags: Array of relevant tags (max 4)
